data.text: Common domesticated species of creatures found throughout the galaxy.
Rare, exotic species of creatures found throughout the galaxy.
Bacta is a thick, gelatinous substance with seemingly magical healing properties. It helps the body regrow tissue, including nerves, skin, and muscles.

Droids are mechanical beings that possessed artificial intelligence. They are used in a variety of roles and environments, often those considered too menial or too dangerous for other species, but also in fields that require extensive specialization and knowledge.
Common food found throughout the galaxy.
Starships are powered by Rhydonium, a volatile fuel found on the planet Abafar.
A collection of rare and exotic gemstones from throughout the galaxy.
Equipment destined to one of the many heavy operations throughout the galaxy.
Luxury items, affordable only to the elite.
Spice is the name for a type of illicit substance or substances in demand throughout the galaxy.
